data.description: You won't want to wait to see this captivating double master townhome. Nestled in an absolute darling neighborhood filled with charm. As you walk up you are surrounded by meticulously landscaped garden beds. As you enter the home, you step onto the cozy porch with double doors into the foyer. Immediately you focus on the large family room the kitchen sits over. Boosting ample light from the sliders in the family room and large bay window in the kitchen. If you like to cook, this is your home. The kitchen is perfect for making meals for one or utilizing the movable island to dice up a grand meal for your friends and family. Speaking of guests, no one wants them in their personal space. If this is your home you won't have to. Between the kitchen and the dining room is the 3rd bath with shower.  The screened in patio has stunning wood look tile, making it a breeze to maintain. A few steps outside of the patio is a deep storage closet, ideal for bikes, tools and ladders. Heading up stairs you have two oversized sized master bedrooms with ensuite and large walk-in closets.HOA Dues cover: Cable TV, Community pool, tennis courts, basketball courts, internet, main grounds, Sewer, water and trash. Roof is 2019, HVAC 2023, Water heater is tankless, currently zoned for Sutherland elementary, Palm Harbor middle and Palm Harbor University. Centrally located near Crystal Beach, Honeymoon island, downtown Palm Harbor, Tarpon Springs sponge dock, tons of shopping, dining, comedy clubs, and so much more! See virtual tour here..   https://app.docusketch.com/portal/tour/EiuaLN0g
